        <updateDate>2004-02-11T22:02:13Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p>Continuity of Congress Act of 2003 - Authorizes the legislature of each State to enact laws declaring who shall serve in the place of members of the House of Representatives and/or the Senate in the event that one-fourth of either or both Houses of Congress are killed or incapacitated.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
